Connectis - Issue 3
--------------------
Europe's e-business magazine profiles ten young entrepreneurs
shaping the e-commerce terrain, analyses the introduction of WAP
technology into the European arena and offers perspectives on
Europe's burgeoning e-economy - from online IPOs to online education.
http://www.ft.com/connectis/

Participate in the Connectis discussion forum to share your views on
e-business.
http://www.ft.com/forums/connectis/

